{"type": "root", "attrs": {"type": "node", "context": "sop", "internal": "tetstrata", "icon": "SOP/tetstrata", "since": "19.0", "tags": "tetrahedralize, solid object, tet mesh, skin, tissue", "version": null, "namespace": null}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Tet Strata"], "extent": [143, 158]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Creates strata of tetrahedra adjacent to a polygon mesh."], "extent": [158, 223]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The Tet Strata SOP creates strata of tetrahedra that are adjacent to the input polygon mesh. The resulting tet mesh can be used to simulate skin and fat layers in a muscle sim, for example using the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/femsolver", "type": "link", "text": ["FEM Solver"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/femsolver"}, " or the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/vellumsolver", "type": "link", "text": ["Vellum Solver"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/vellumsolver"}, ". Tet Strata turns a polygonal sphere into a hollow ball, whereas ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/tetconform", "type": "link", "text": ["Tet Conform"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/tetconform"}, " turns a polygonal sphere into a solid ball."], "extent": [223, 643]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The tetrahedra share the polygon points. This SOP is not limited to triangular polygons; it may be used with quadrangles as well."], "extent": [643, 774]}, {"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"type": "tip", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [774, 779], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["For building good quality simulation meshes, we recommend that you apply a ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/remesh", "type": "link", "text": ["Remesh SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/remesh"}, " to your polygonal geometry before Tet Strata."], "extent": [779, 934]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"level": 1, "id": "parameters", "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [934, 946], "body": [{"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Sizing"], "extent": [946, 960], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Layer Depth"], "extent": [960, 978], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["This determine the depth of the tet layer, relative to the normal directions of the input polygons."], "extent": [978, 1087]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Output Geometry"], "extent": [1087, 1109], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Preserve Input Geometry"], "extent": [1109, 1139], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["All input primitives are preserved in the output. New tetrahedra are added and may share points with the input primitives."], "extent": [1139, 1271]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/tetembed", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/tetembed"}], "extent": [1271, 1293]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/tetconform", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/tetconform"}], "extent": [1293, 1317]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/remesh", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/remesh"}], "extent": [1317, 1337]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/divide", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/divide"}], "extent": [1337, 1357]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/polyreduce", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/polyreduce"}], "extent": [1357, 1381]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/vdbfrompolygons", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/vdbfrompolygons"}], "extent": [1381, 1410]}], "container": true}], "text": "Parameters"}], "title": ["Tet Strata"], "summary": ["Creates strata of tetrahedra adjacent to a polygon mesh."]}